text: The Mali women's national under-18 and under-19 is a national basketball team of Mali and is governed by the Fédération Malienne de Basketball. It represents Mali in international under-19 and under-18 (under age 19 and under age 18) women's basketball competitions. ==See also== * Mali women's national basketball team * Mali women's national under-17 basketball team ==References== under Category:Women's national under-18 basketball teams Category:Women's national under-19 basketball teams
title: Mali women's national under-18 basketball team
